<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.6">
<l>eṇṇeyk kuṭattai yuruṭṭi yiḷampiḷḷai kiḷḷi yeḻuppik</l>
<l>kaṇṇaip puraṭṭi viḻittuk kaḻaikaṇṭu ceyyum parāṉē</l>
<l>yuṇṇak kaṉikaḷ taruva ṉolikaṭa lōtanīr pōlē</l>
<l>vaṇṇa maḻakiya nampī mañcaṉa māṭanī vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord! [You] who imitates an elephant goad [i.e.causes mischief],</l>
<l>spinning the pots of gingili oil, waking and pinching young children,</l>
<l>opening and rolling [your] eyes.</l>
<l>Beautiful lord, you with a complexion</l>
<l>like the flooding water of the roaring sea,</l>
<l>I will give you fruit to eat.</l>
<l>Come take [your] ceremonial bath!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
